arget=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F171441_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png&h=bb404f5b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b000df203ad5c5909b30af4ed7d2d77b500af15d","tid":1963800,"uid":48124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"政府以20億購50萬張機票 為航空公司提供現金流<br />\n08.04.2020 19:18<br />\n<br />\n政府宣布機管局會動用20億元支援航空業，運輸及房屋局長陳帆指，會為本港航空公司購買50萬張「遠期」機票，為航空公司在疫情期間提供現金流，機票會留待日後疫情結束後，吸引旅客來港或本港居民出遊；亦會為航空公司的大型客機提供100萬元維修津貼，但承認相比每架飛機一年6000萬元的維修費只屬皮毛。另外超過100名僱員的航空業相關企業，會獲300萬元資助；少於100名僱員的企業可獲100萬元資助。<br />\n<br />\n機管局亦會向相關企業暫時購置它們擁有的機場後勤設施，為企業提供現金流，同時繼續為企業設免租期，待疫情過去，企業可以購回這些設施。陳帆形容有關措施具有創意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279597&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279597%26csid%3D261_341&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBWrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=83e31924\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279597&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"75b24ce7cd11be058b54e8411ea22f187d6ed7ad","tid":1963800,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d97d3053b2822ca4f23ef1587391dc82e6da7e3","tid":1963800,"uid":56084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"屌 真係on9 50000張可以做到d乜 on99 比哂國泰一間都冇撚用啦 得個十幾億最多咪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:34:40.000Z","msg":"你就想比晒國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab109006edd4d063313fc1290c7acd4d2629d028","tid":1963800,"uid":50386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:35:15.000Z","msg":"陳帆形容有關措施具有創意。<br />\n<br />\n自己讚自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl